snippet.title: Mutants: Genesis : LIVE DEV #1 ! 🧬
snippet.description:
We hosted our very first live dev on December 20th! 
This meeting was an opportunity to present the game deeply and exchange with the Mutants: Genesis team. Thank you so much for being with us, we hope you had a great time!

⏺ Want to follow us? 
🔵 Facebook : https://bit.ly/MutantsGenesisCCG
🔵 Twiter : https://bit.ly/MutantsGenesisTwitter
🔵 Steam :  https://bit.ly/MutantsGenesis1

#MutantsGenesis #CelsiusOnline
